Usage: view_package_results [-help] [-result_file <string>] -type <string>
                            [-workspace <string>]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-result_file <string>   # <result file .xml for static or .cur for dynamic>
                        # (string, optional)
-type <string>          # <specify one type of dc|ac|tran|thermal>
                        # (string, required)
-workspace <string>     # <package analysis workspace> (string, optional)